title: Ep. - 543 - IDENTICAL TWINS WHO JUST MET, MOLLY AND EMILY FROM AMAZING RACE RYAN BAILEY REVIEWS KARDASHIANS ON HULU
description:
Emily Bushnell and Molly Sinert are identical twins who only met a year ago, and are competing in season 34 of The Amazing Race. They tell their incredible story of finding one another.

 

Ryan Bailey from So Good It’s Bad podcast helps Kate review the season premiere of Kardashians on Hulu.
